shamitabh is a 2015 indian satirical film written and directed by r. balki . the film features amitabh bachchan , dhanush and akshara haasan , in her debut , in the lead roles . the film is jointly produced by sunil lulla , balki , rakesh jhunjhunwala , r. k. damani , amitabh bachchan , abhishek bachchan , sunil manchanda and dhanush under their respective production banners . ilaiyaraaja composed the soundtrack album and background score , while cinematography was handled by p. c. sreeram . the film released to positive reviews with critics praising dhanush and amitabh 's performances .